claim.claim-text:
13. A server comprising:
a chassis;
a single printed circuit assembly mounted interior to the chassis, the printed circuit assembly further comprising a planar backplane adapted for operation in a horizontal orientation;
at least one disk drive attached in a vertical orientation on planar backplane; and
at least one four-bar linkage coupled to the planar backplane and adapted to insert and remove disk drives from the disk drive connectors, enabling the disk drives to be installed and removed via a horizontal motion and engaged and disengaged via a vertical motion.
